7 (c) The lead employee or coordinator who manages the Deaf Culture Digital
8 Library shall be:
9 (1) A deaf or hard of hearing individual; and
10 (2) Knowledgeable and experienced concerning issues affecting deaf and
11 hard of hearing individuals.
12 (D) FOR FISCAL YEAR 2026 AND EACH FISCAL YEAR THEREAFTER, THE
13 GOVERNOR SHALL INCLUDE IN THE ANNUAL BUDGET BILL AN APPROPRIATION OF
14 $450,000 TO THE DEAF CULTURE DIGITAL LIBRARY.
15 (E) THE DEAF CULTURE DIGITAL LIBRARY SHALL SUBMIT ITS ANNUAL
16 OPERATING BUDGET TO THE STATE LIBRARY AGENCY ON OR BEFORE JUNE 1 EACH
17 YEAR.
18 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
